modules.description: This module provides functions to search for authors, publications, and venues via the DBLP API, returning structured data such as author names and URLs, publication metadata including titles and DOIs, and venue names and types. It supports querying with optional hit limits and offers a utility to convert publication records into string representations. Concrete use cases include retrieving a list of publications by a specific author, finding venues by acronym, and extracting BibTeX entries for citations.
